So we (Me Ben Han Lu Nobbzey) went to see The Rasmus last night...it was AWESOME! We got right to the second row from the front and were ssooo close to the stage and the band.They came on stage to the Funeral Song and everyone went WILD! I'm not giving this gig a good enough write up or propper justice because I can't describe it, all I can say was that it was totally amazingly awesome lol. Lauri looked cute as usual (hehe). This girl had her arm signed by him but we weren't there when he signed her :(. I wanted signing!! And at the end Nobbzey managed to get the guitarists pick! The support band (Happylife) were great too, the guy with the long blonde hair rocked, all the rest were a bit grumpy (lol) but anyway they have their single coming out in September, I have to go buy it! The blonde dude gave me his guitar pick so it's up on my little notice board thingie. So after the gig we got merchandise and went to the Pit and Pendulum for a few drinks which was funky. Californication came on so me and Han sung along to it even though our voices were going from screaming the lyrics at the gig and screaming at Lauri. Han said she'd send me the piccies that she got from the gig, I can't wait to get them. But anyway back to the Pit. We left but we missed our tram anyway so we went to Mc Donalds for something to eat and these guys were being morons yelling "Goth" at us (which if he had intelligence he would see that I am neither a goth or a punk I'm me, a little mix of both) so we just laughed at them lol. *sigh* such a great night! I hope New Found Glory are as good on Wednesday. Ah I forgot to post my GCSE results! I'm quite pleased with them, they mean I can still go to college so all is good in the world lol.
So here they are:
English - B
English Language - C
Religious Studies - B
Geography - B
History - C
Graphics - D
Double award Science - DD
Maths - F
French - C
Not the most brainiest results but I don't mind. As long as I got the college grades I wasn't going to be bothered. I'm still on a high from the gig last night so I'm going to be bouncing off the walls all day whilst listening to Dead Letters. Oh and maybe sleeping because I didn't get too much of it last night. I'll post again soon when something eventful and exciting happens hehe, c ya! xxx

Hey ppls. Wow I haven't updated in aaagggeeessss, bad me. Not really got anything majour to report tho, had a fun summer but now just getting really nervous about results *eek!*. And getting excited about college, new place, new people, new friends etc. Work still sucks but hey you win some you loose some, I'd never give it up though, I love the money too much teehee. Aww just had a really good laugh over the time Jess' P.E knickers flew into the road, good mermories!! So anyway about love life, currently free single and lovin' it hehe. I know people usually say that only because they're upset and lonely about not having someone but i seriously mean it, who needs guys? I did date this guy called Sean for a short time but just don't go there, not my type. Results in two days...I'll post them even if they're crap which I really hope they're not! Ooohh yer, got my lip done too *beams with pride* I love it hehe. Anyway I'm off, bye byeeee! xxx

From Go-Quiz.com So anyway I havent updated in aaggeess!! Too much stuff going on like work, exams etc. Went clubbing down Notts last night, i got ssssooo pissed it was unbelieveable. I personally blame the buy one get one free cocktails. And the shots. And all the rest. So Seans Dad wouldn't let me get the tram back by myself cos I was totally pissed so he gave me a lift home and I said some bloody stupid stuff to him. Like how speed bumps made me need a wee....*blush* God I'm so stupid when I'm drunk. Oh well. So nothing else going off today. Got work later but only for 4 hours. Should have a laugh about last night with the girls anyway. Urgh gotta go to my Dads this weekend too! Thats three weekends in a row!! Thats pissed me off big time. Oh well work all weekend so I don't have to see him much. I wonder if I can see Sean this weekend at all...I hope so cos I miss him already!! Errr...nothing else to say I don't think. God life's boring. Oh well. Oooohhh it's Litha soon!! *dances about* Me and Cherise were gonna go see the solstice at stonehenge but my Dad can't give us a lift down there after all :( I'm gonna go iron my work uniform now *sigh* au revoir xxx p.s i almost forgot does anyone wanna come see blink 182 with me 4 my birthday!?

God the leaving ceremony was so sad I cried all the way through it! But onto happier things I went into Notts after to get my handcuffs [hehe kinky!!] and saw Katie and Keeley it was such a laugh we went into Ann Summers and Keeley started lookin at the dildo's but then we got asked to leave 'cos we weren't 18! We went to Debenhams too and tried on loads of dresses it was so much fun! Got the party in a bit so I'm getting ready putting loads of concealer on this huge spot near my mouth *growls* it would show up a day before the prom!! So tonight should be good but I have to go early 'cos of work in the mornin'. Such a busy day tomorrow but it should be great! Everythings ready for the prom I even chose my hairstyle but it's a surprise so the people who already know don't blab! One bad thing though is that I don't know whether I can go down the rig on Sunday or not but I'll try my bloody bestest!! Anyway I'm gonna go now tata! xxx

Omg today was so sad! We left school and it was a fun day but when the bell went at the end of the day and we were hugging goodbye and everything we were all crying, I couldn't stop! Walked home with Ron Helen and Aaron though which was nice. Today was really fun though people wrote really sweet stuff on my shirt and all we did was prat about all day. German was the best though (I don't even do the subject!!) but we had a right laugh with the taking pictures of Heaton etc. I took my camera too so I got goodbye messages on that from everyone which is really sweet! Leaving Ceremony tomorrow too...I'm gonna bawl my eyes out!! I don't wanna leave everyone I'll miss them all ssoo soo much. We got Mrs Hatcher a massive bouquet of flowers, she seemed dead chuffed! We always used to slag her off but she wasn't such a bad form tutor after all. Aww assembily this morning was really sweet too 'cos mrs Costin gave us a really sweet little speech and she was welling up which made us well up and it was just a generally all round fun/sad day. I'll miss school.

God I havent updated in ages so here goes. I'm kinda glad I couldn't make it to Bec K's party last night it sounded kinda bad from what I've heard (everyone crying, lads being total dicks Ironville people coming etc.) I got the job at Matalan which is good news so i start on saturday. Only 4 more days left at school now...it's such a scarey and sad but happy thought at the same time. I will miss everyone so much! The prom on Saturday too, it'll be really depressing for me and Jess so I'm coming wearing waterproof mascara for when i start crying (Jess is doing the same i think.) But the party on the park on Friday night should be good...should be 'cos after what I heard about Bec K's party things better be better for this one! Feeling kinda depressed today things wont heal after so long and i hate it but theres nothing I can do to make the feelings stop. Went into town today, got a bank account set up and did a bit of shopping. I got my photo's developed yesterday they are so nice I love them to bits! I got two special cute frames for two of them because they are so nice (its the group one with like everyone on it and the one of jess Shaun James and Aiden). That reminds me Aiden hasn't given me my chain back yet after like a month and I'm really pissed off about it now 'cos it's my fave ever. Grrr god don't you just hate males sometimes?? Anyway I'm gonna piss off now bye bye xx

Hey. I'm feeling kinda pissed off actually cos matalan still hasnt got back to me *growls at them* i need the bloody job! But anyway nothing much really went off today, Han's gone on holiday lucky sod lol. Hope she has a gd time. So nothing to say so I'll go lol xxx

So yesterday I had my job interview. I was bloody well shittin myself I was so nervous. But yer I think it went well, they said that they would get back to me in a few days or maybe even today but I don't think that they will call me today after all. Eh well, just another few days of waiting nervously to find out if I have the job or not. So nothing much else has happened. I took my digital cam into school today to take photo's for my leaving book, they all rock!! I love all my mates *hugs to you all* I'd be dead without them (especially Jess cos she's always here to listen and make me laugh). I'll miss everyone so much tho. Only 13 more school days left until we leave...creepy thought. So thats all I have to say really...just waiting for the call... byeee xx

Hey everyone. Wow seems ages since I've updated. So anyway went up to Yorkshire for the weekend, I thought it was gonna be really bad but it was quite good actually. Went to the film and photography museum which was awesome. It was just like totally my thing. So anyway then I went to get my prom shoes and got some really kewl italian boots aswell. So anyway there was this really kewl exhibition by Luc Delahaye called Winterreise that was really moving. Like he went round really poor parts of Russia and went into peoples homes and lives and stuff and it is sad but it makes you realise how fortunate you are. So anyway nothing else to say, I'm pretty tired since I just got up. I was s'posed to be going out with Fee today but he didn't text me back when I asked him if we still were so I'll probs be stuck in at home. Oh well. Oh yay I can't believe I forgot this...I have a job interview with Matalan tomorrow!!!! YAYEEEEEEEEE. Ok I have to calm down but I need this job so badly. Anyway bye byeeeee xxx

Hi, I haven't updated for a few days so yer. Been too depressed and emotional and crazy. So yesterday he wouldn't leave me alone mutting stuff like I was a fucking ho and stuff and they were laughing at me in the hall so I just snapped. I started going really crazy. I sat down on the floor in the hall and started scraping my nails across my wrists. I scared myself but couldn't stop. My Dad phoned when I got in to see how I was and I ended up telling him everything. How he wont leave me alone and how he said and did all of those things and about how I tried to kill myself. I thought my Dad would yell at me but he didn't he was really nice about it. I just hope I feel normal again. I really want to feel normal. But hey I suppose I can wait. Whats a few more years of feeling like this? You never know, I could be gone by then. I don't even know.

Hello! So today was just a typical school day, nothig much went off. Hannah and Jess were gettin all depressed at lunch, I hate seeing them both so upset :(, makes me upset too. So anyway when I got home I had like an hour and a half long bath hehe, I think I dosed off for a bit :P. Twas gooood anywho. I shall depart now. Au revoir *waves*

Bonjour peoples. I think I'm gonna be dragged into Notts again today (not of my own accord but hey). Eh I have money so I'll probs find some nice things (lol) to blow it on. I think another trip to Yum Yum is in order lol, not for stickers this time though! My leaving book is now covered, not that it's a bad thing but yesterday I brought 5 sticker packs!! I must have spent about a tenner just on stickers lolol. No one online, apart from Elliot the lovable retard lol, it's probs cos I'm up way too early. Hey I could go and get something peirced today my mum said I could have my ear done at the top but we were both pissed at the time so who knows lol. I might just get it done anyway. I shall depart now and update later...tis a good plan... Tata xxx

Hey! So today I went into Notts with Jess to see the Butterfly Effect, which totally rocks.
